N2  - The venture team is an attempt to avoid bureaucratic obstacles to new product innovation. A study of 21 venture team failures revealed that concerns with financial costs, marketing problems, and personnel or organizational factors were among the major causes for failures. In-depth field interviews revealed many of the underlying operational reasons for the venture failures.
